 -- Horst Miller <horst@datahammer.de>  Wed, 21 Apr 2014 10:04:34 +0900

7yuv (2.1) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Add support for YUV422 10-bit V210 (OpenGL mode only)
  * Predefined resolutions can be customized in Json config
  * Bugfix: div0 when both scaling and grid size are small

 -- Horst Miller <horst@datahammer.de>  Wed, 19 Apr 2014 10:04:34 +0900

7yuv (2.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Json-format config files.
  * Optional OpenGL rendering in graphics mode
  * Scaling in graphics mode
  * RGB channel filtering
  * Color schemes for graphics mode
  * YUV411 support
  * RGBA raw palette format support
  * "Screen copy" for text modes (render to text buffer)
  * misc bug fixes

 -- Horst Miller <horst@datahammer.de>  Wed, 15 Apr 2014 10:04:34 +0900

7yuv (1.8) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Configurable mode colour schemes.
  * Fix AYUV rendering (Y and U channel were swapped).
  * Detect AYUV raw graphics format based on .ayuv file extension.
  * Test bar generation for packed AYUV, YUV444, YUV422 formats.
  * Show CSD in filer, when opening window with new file.
  * In-place graphics format conversion (although not all combinations supported).
  * Some new icons

 -- Horst Miller <horst@datahammer.de>  Wed, 13 Feb 2013 10:04:34 +0900

